{"tid":832800,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"球場失意情場更失意！「山神」坦言已失戀...","createTime":"2018-09-23T05:01:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T07:09:32.000Z","uid":161790,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d73a298b9d818079a246a7d0cde30a7e1c71eff4","tid":832800,"uid":161790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T05:01:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/23/125922_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F125922_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e101c970&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n山齊士這一年過得不順利<br />\n自打一月份轉會曼聯以來，山齊士的表現一直不盡如人意。對比阿仙奴時期，如今的智利人的戰鬥力好像掉了一檔。加上英媒不斷炒作山齊士英超第一高薪，他身上的壓力也非常大。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/23/125949_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F125949_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5f47f438&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/23/125956_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F125956_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=26f3157e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如今球場失意的智利人在情場上也受挫了。山齊士在自己的Instagram上宣佈自己和女友瑪雅-洛迪古斯分手了。山齊士寫道：「我祝你一切都好，我很高興遇見你並和你分享美麗的時刻，但我們決定每個人都要追尋自己的道路和夢想。我希望那些不明真相就出口傷人的人尊重我們，因為這一切的背後還有家庭和孩子。尊重。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/23/130031_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F130031_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9070407a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國媒體《每日郵報》表示，這一年對於山齊士而言過得比較艱難。一月份他離開阿仙奴轉會曼聯，簽下了大合約，但是表現時好時壞，受到了不少批評和質疑。如今自己也和女友分手了。不知經歷這次情感變化後，是否會刺激山齊士在球場上大發神威。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/23/130102_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F130102_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0c118a50&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19b31c97362783932781587888ed18710d89c73b","tid":832800,"uid":161790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T05:02:17.000Z","msg":"山神終於可以專心踢波"},{"pid":"ee3fd06c425d2fc0750e7653b78fa2382127a6c8","tid":832800,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T05:04:26.000Z","msg":"人工都少左<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc1334634728dcd97cd441cc839fa477cf1e52a4","tid":832800,"uid":161790,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T05:05:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/23/130506_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F130506_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=55af0e85&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c78b75b236d9410afb215dee0611517358a0b9f0","tid":832800,"uid":61018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"19b31c97362783932781587888ed18710d89c73b","tid":832800,"uid":161790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T05:02:17.000Z","msg":"山神終於可以專心踢波"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T05:05:13.000Z","msg":"專心食女"},{"pid":"9bce6973a044abf97753ff242a1582754b6dc9bf","tid":832800,"uid":161790,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"c78b75b236d9410afb215dee0611517358a0b9f0","tid":832800,"uid":61018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"19b31c97362783932781587888ed18710d89c73b","tid":832800,"uid":161790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T05:02:17.000Z","msg":"山神終於可以專心踢波"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T05:05:13.000Z","msg":"專心食女"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T05:07:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ese